                <m>f(x)=\frac{3}{x-2}</m>
              </li>
              <li>
                <m>f(x)=x^{3}-1</m>
              </li>
              <li>Find the inverse function of <m>f(x)=\frac{1}{x-1}.</m> Use a graphing utility to find its domain and range. Write the domain and range in interval notation.</li>
            </ol>
